entry.description: "TRANCHE KEY: sFUC/lcotxPXpvTlwfKgO6H5uRKHvMq4N7COE6W+oj6yvdMIsFHoPDbKrNOzQQYKvd72uofgyzaw5smpyYpftPp131AAAAAAAAACyw== Original data file: Winter global 1.mgf. From Tranche: {{i}}Data files include .raw files generated using an Orbitrap XL mass spectrometer and associated .mgf files generated using DTASuperCharge from the MaxQuant software package. Files described as -global- contain mass spectrometry runs for peptides enriched for phosphorylated peptides, files described as pTyr contain mass spectrometry runs for peptides enriched for phosphorylated tyrosine. All experiments use alternating CID/HCD fragmentation MS/MS scans to generate sequence ions and iTRAQ ions respectively for each peptide.{{/i}}"
